propDescriptions.component: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.components: The components used for each slot inside the MenuItem. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.componentsProps: The props used for each slot inside the MenuItem.
propDescriptions.disabled: If true, the menu item will be disabled.
propDescriptions.label: A text representation of the menu item's content. Used for keyboard text navigation matching.
